longBusinessSummary: MBH Corporation PLC, an investment holding company, operates in the education and construction service sectors in the United Kingdom, Oceania, Asia, and North America. It offers vocational training to early year sectors, as well as health, social, management, beauty, and sports education sectors; educational software solutions; commercial interior fit-out and construction contractor services; and aged care residential and taxi services. The company also engages in the sale of new and used caravans; and real estate brokerage, investment, and commercial funding activities. MBH Corporation PLC was incorporated in 2016 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
